  "chapter": {
    "number": 27,
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "content": [
          "The LORD Is My Salvation"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "hebrew_subtitle",
        "content": [
          "Of David."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 1,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The LORD is my light and my salvation—",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "whom shall I fear?",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "The LORD is the stronghold of my life—",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "whom shall I dread?",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 2,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "When the wicked came upon me to devour my flesh,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "my enemies and foes stumbled and fell.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 3,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Though an army encamps around me,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "my heart will not fear;",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "though a war breaks out against me,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "I will keep my trust.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 4,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "One thing I have asked of the LORD;",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "this is what I desire:",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "to dwell in the house of the LORD",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "all the days of my life,",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "to gaze on the beauty of the LORD",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "and seek Him in His temple.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 5,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "For in the day of trouble",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "He will hide me in His shelter;",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "He will conceal me under the cover of His tent;",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "He will set me high upon a rock.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 6,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Then my head will be held high",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "above my enemies around me.",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "At His tabernacle I will offer sacrifices with shouts of joy;",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "I will sing and make music to the LORD.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 7,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Hear, O LORD, my voice when I call;",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "be merciful and answer me.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 8,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "My heart said, “Seek His face.”",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "Your face, O LORD, I will seek.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 9,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Hide not Your face from me,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "nor turn away Your servant in anger.",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "You have been my helper;",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "do not leave me or forsake me,",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "O God of my salvation.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 10,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Though my father and mother forsake me,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "the LORD will receive me.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 11,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Teach me Your way, O LORD,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "and lead me on a level path,",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "because of my oppressors.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 12,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Do not hand me over to the will of my foes,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "for false witnesses rise up against me,",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "breathing out violence.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 13,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Still I am certain to see",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "the goodness of the LORD",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "in the land of the living.",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 14,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Wait patiently for the LORD;",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "be strong and courageous.",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "lineBreak": true
          },
          {
            "text": "Wait patiently for the LORD!",
            "poem": 1
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "footnotes": []
  },
